Process called "less_equal" that takes x1 as NDArray.NDArray and x2 as NDArray.NDArray returns NDArray.NDArray:
    Return NDArray.less_equal with a as x1 and b as x2

Process called "greater" that takes x1 as NDArray.NDArray and x2 as NDArray.NDArray returns NDArray.NDArray:
