Process called "logical_or" that takes x1 as NDArray.NDArray and x2 as NDArray.NDArray returns NDArray.NDArray:
    Return NDArray.logical_or with a as x1 and b as x2

Process called "logical_not" that takes x as NDArray.NDArray returns NDArray.NDArray:
    Return NDArray.logical_not with array as x

Process called "logical_xor" that takes x1 as NDArray.NDArray and x2 as NDArray.NDArray returns NDArray.NDArray:
    Return NDArray.logical_xor with a as x1 and b as x2

Process called "isnan" that takes x as NDArray.NDArray returns NDArray.NDArray:
