Process called "ascontiguousarray" that takes a as NDArray.NDArray and dtype as Optional[NDArray.DataType] returns NDArray.NDArray:
    Let target_dtype be dtype or a.dtype
    If NDArray.is_contiguous with array as a and dtype as target_dtype:
        Return a
    Otherwise:
        Return NDArray.make_contiguous with array as a and dtype as target_dtype

